description:
**Description**
Energy consumption, climate, and wastewater characteristics of Melbourne eastern wastewater treatment plant for preiod of six years (2014-2019).
https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Faramarz-Bagherzadeh-2

**Steps to reproduce**
This dataset is a combination (inner join) of open access data produced by Melbourne water and Melbourne airport weather station. Power consumption, Hydraulic, biological, and climate data are merged by the record date column (day/month/year).   

**Institutions**
Politechnika Gdanska
Categories
Environmental Analysis, Machine Learning, Wastewater, Energy Consumption

**License**
CC BY 4.0

Link : https://data.mendeley.com/datasets/pprkvz3vbd/1
title: Full Scale Waste Water Treatment Plant Data
